    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA197-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu varaivu nīṭa āṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaḷait tōḻi āṟṟuvittatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante encouraged HER who was unable to bear it when the marriage was delayed.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA197">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            tōḷē toṭinekiḻn taṉavē nutalē</l>
<l>            pīrivar malariṟ pacappūrn taṉṟē</l>
<l>            kaṇṇun taṇpaṉi vaikiṉa vaṉṉō</l>
<l>            teḷintaṉa maṉṟa tēyareṉ ṉuyireṉa</l>
<l>            vāḻal vāḻi tōḻi nīniṉ </l>
<l>            tāḻntoli katuppiṉ vīḻnta kāloṭu</l>
<l>            vaṇṭupaṭu putumala ruṇṭuṟait tarīiya</l>
<l>            perumaṭa makaḷir muṉkaic ciṟukōṟ</l>
<l>            polantoṭi pōla miṉṉik kaṇaṅko</l>
<l>            ḷiṉṉicai muraci ṉiraṅki maṉṉa </l>
<l>            reyilūr paḵṟōl pōlac</l>
<l>            ceṉmaḻai tavaḻumavar naṉmalai nāṭṭē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>“[My] shoulders, the bracelets have become loose.</l>
<l rend="indent4">		[My] forehead,</l>
<l>pallor crept up like the climbing blossoms of the Pīr.</l>
<l>And [my] eyes,<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">tōḷē - nutalē - kaṇṇum</term>: T.V.G. sees here an enumeration were the last member is marked by -<term xml:lang="ta">um</term>.</note> they were kept in cool dew, alas.</l>
<l>We have understood, indeed, that my life is dwindling.”</l>
<l>– don't be overwhelmed, oh you<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">tōḻi nī</term>: the ‘you’ has to be taken as a second vocative.</note>, friend.</l>
<l>His land's good mountains are covered with moving clouds,</l>
<l rend="indent3">	as the many shields of the king's fortified village,</l>
<l rend="indent2">	sounding with the groupwise pleasing sounds of the drum,</l>
<l rend="indent2">	flashing like golden bracelets in small rows(?)</l>
<l rend="indent3">	on the forearms of women of great inexperience,</l>
<l rend="indent">	so as to bring new blossoms visited by bees to the drinking ghat,</l>
<l rend="indent">	together with wind that descended into your hanging dense hair.</l>
        </lg>
